A Superbian and an Invidian
were arguing at the auction
over there just now.

rows.label: tlk41300011_02_msg0002
rows.name:
Why do they have to clash over
even the smallest things...?

rows.label: tlk41300011_02_msg0003
rows.name:
I just hope it doesn't lead to Superbia
and Invidia starting a war...

rows.label: tlk41300011_02_msg0004
rows.name:
Because only a handful of people
would be happy if a war began.
